cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.IR, cs.NE 

This paper deals with natural language processing and machine learning techniques to model affective interpretations of words. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also proposes a new model for word embeddings, which is a common topic in machine learning and deep learning research, making cs.LG (Machine Learning) another likely category. The paper also involves the use of neural networks, which is a common technique in artificial intelligence research, making cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) another possible category. The paper also involves information retrieval techniques, which could make cs.IR (Information Retrieval) a possible category. Finally, the paper involves the use of neural networks for prediction tasks, which could make cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) a possible category.
